headline: Trane Technologies (TT): 3 Reasons We Love This Stock
summary: Trane Technologies currently trades at $434.41 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 326% since July 2020, more than tripling the S&P 500’s 93.9% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 11.7% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
